---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@components/container.astro";
import Sectionhead from "@components/sectionhead.astro";
---

<Layout title="Resources">
  <Container>
    <Sectionhead>
      <Fragment slot="title">Resources</Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">
        <p class="text-lg mt-4 text-slate-600 px-0 md:px-4 lg:px-10">
          Organization documents, tech-stack, operational resources, and FAQ. <br/>
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg mt-4 text-left md:text-justify text-slate-600 px-0 md:px-4 lg:px-10">
          The Space is an education-focused organization and social hub, dedicated to transparency, integrity, and member advocacy.
          Rooted in bitcoin and the open-source movement, we value freedom and working publicly.
          These principles guide our responsible treasury management and operations.
          See the documentation below for more detail.
        </p>
      </Fragment>
    </Sectionhead>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-10 mt-12 mb-20">
      <!-- Member Resources Section -->
      <section class="card-hover-effect bg-white border-4 border-[#ffffff] rounded-lg p-6">
        <div class="section-title flex items-center">
          <img src="/assets/branding/Logos/TheSpace_Logos_Symbol_2.webp" alt="The Space Icon" loading="eager" class="w-9 h-9 mr-2"/>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold leading-snug tracking-tight">Member Resources</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-500 mt-3">Key information for members.</p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-4 text-lg text-[#bebebe]">
          <li><a href="/assets/resources/DRAFT.pdf" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">Member Handbook</a></li>
          <li><a href="/assets/resources/Building_Conduct_Code_REV001.pdf" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">Building Code of Conduct</a></li>
          <li><a href="/assets/resources/Social_vs_CoWorking_Tiers_REV001.pdf" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">Member Tier Breakdown</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://nextcloud.denver.space/s/8J4cdpaBd2XmZrp" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">Affiliate Programs & Offerings</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- Tech Stack Section -->
      <section class="card-hover-effect bg-white border-4 border-[#ffffff] rounded-lg p-6">
        <div class="section-title flex items-center">
          <img src="/assets/branding/Logos/TheSpace_Logos_Symbol_2.webp" alt="The Space Icon" loading="eager" class="w-9 h-9 mr-2"/>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold leading-snug tracking-tight">Tech Stack</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-500 mt-3">Sovereign tools that run The Space.</p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-4 text-lg text-[#bebebe]">
          <li><a href="/assets/resources/DRAFT.pdf" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">Our FOSS Infrastructure</a></li>
          <li><a href="/assets/resources/DRAFT.pdf" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">Space Nextcloud Handbook</a></li>
          <li><a href="/assets/resources/DRAFT.pdf" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">Official COMMS Channels</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com/denver-space" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">The Space GitHub</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- Transparency Section -->
      <section class="card-hover-effect bg-white border-4 border-[#ffffff] rounded-lg p-6">
        <div class="section-title flex items-center">
          <img src="/assets/branding/Logos/TheSpace_Logos_Symbol_2.webp" alt="The Space Icon" loading="eager" class="w-9 h-9 mr-2"/>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold leading-snug tracking-tight">Transparency</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-500 mt-3">Don't trust. Verify.</p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-4 text-lg text-[#bebebe]">
          <li><a href="/assets/resources/Executed Bylaws_REV001.pdf" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">Executed Bylaws</a></li>
          <li><a href="/assets/resources/DRAFT.pdf" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">Record Retention</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://nextcloud.denver.space/s/RwdNJz9ogMJtzsz" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">Board Meeting Minutes</a></li>
          <li><a href="/assets/resources/DRAFT.pdf" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">Photography & Anon Privacy</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- Operations Section -->
      <section class="card-hover-effect bg-white border-4 border-[#ffffff] rounded-lg p-6">
        <div class="section-title flex items-center">
          <img src="/assets/branding/Logos/TheSpace_Logos_Symbol_2.webp" alt="The Space Icon" loading="eager" class="w-9 h-9 mr-2"/>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold leading-snug tracking-tight">Operations</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-500 mt-3">How we operate.</p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-4 text-lg text-[#bebebe]">
          <li><a href="/assets/resources/DRAFT.pdf" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">Elections & Governance</a></li>
          <li><a href="/assets/resources/DRAFT.pdf" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">Education & Events</a></li>
          <li><a href="/assets/resources/DRAFT.pdf" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">Committees</a></li>
          <li><a href="/assets/resources/DRAFT.pdf" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">Self-Hosting</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- Treasury Section -->
      <section class="card-hover-effect bg-white border-4 border-[#ffffff] rounded-lg p-6">
        <div class="section-title flex items-center">
          <img src="/assets/branding/Logos/TheSpace_Logos_Symbol_2.webp" alt="The Space Icon" loading="eager" class="w-9 h-9 mr-2"/>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold leading-snug tracking-tight">Treasury</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-500 mt-3">Satoshi Status.</p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-4 text-lg text-[#bebebe]">
          <li><a href="/assets/resources/DRAFT.pdf" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">Treasury Reserve Policy</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://treasury.denver.space" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">Proof of Reserves Dashboard</a></li>
          <li><a href="/assets/resources/How_DuesAre_Spent_REV001.pdf" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">How Dues are Spent</a></li>
          <li><a href="/assets/resources/DRAFT.pdf" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">501(c)(3) Non Profit Info</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- Building The Space Section -->
      <section class="card-hover-effect bg-white border-4 border-[#ffffff] rounded-lg p-6">
        <div class="section-title flex items-center">
          <img src="/assets/branding/Logos/TheSpace_Logos_Symbol_2.webp" alt="The Space Icon" loading="eager" class="w-9 h-9 mr-2"/>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold leading-snug tracking-tight">The Space</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-500 mt-3">Bitcoin Hub Blueprint and Details.</p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-4 text-lg text-[#bebebe]">
          <li><a href="/assets/resources/our-journey.pdf" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">Roadmap & History</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://nextcloud.denver.space/s/6mT8GfZy5DdRkbY" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">Branding Package</a></li>
          <li><a href="/assets/resources/The_Space_EventVenue_Deck.pdf" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">Venue and Event Booking</a></li>
          <li><a href="/assets/resources/The Space - Business Development Deck-5.pdf" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">Business Development Deck</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </Container>

  <!-- FAQ Section with Gradient Background -->
  <div class="faq-gradient py-12 mt-0">
    <Container>
      <section class="px-0 md:px-4 lg:px-10">
        <h2 class="text-4xl mt-12 mb-12 font-bold text-white">FAQ</h2>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <p class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-200 mb-4">What is The Space?</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">The Space is a bitcoin citadel and social hub, focused on education, collaboration, and community building.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <p class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-200 mb-4">Where is The Space?</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Our physical location is in the heart of Denver, CO at 3700 N Franklin St. Accessibile by Denver Light Rail public transport from the Denver Airport. A short walk from the 38th and Blake A line train station.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <p class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-200 mb-4">Why should I become a Member?</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">The Space is focused on education and community building within the bitcoin ecosystem. Become a member to learn, build relationships, socialize and work with the brightest in the industry.
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <p class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-200 mb-4">Do I need to be a member to physically access The Space?</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Yes. Only members get regular access to our physical location. Free and ticketed events are open to the public.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <p class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-200 mb-4">What kinds of events and presentations will you have?</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Education is the core pillar of our mission. The Space will host events ranging from novice friendly to in-the-weeds deep dives. We also host workshops, panel discussions and high signal summits and conferences.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <p class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-200 mb-4">How can I become a member?</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">You can apply for membership by filling out the member application form. We'll follow up to get you onboarded!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <p class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-200 mb-4">How many members are there?</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">We have 55 incredible Founding Members, with new members joining regularly. As currently defined in our Bylaws, The Space is limited to a maximum of 210 members.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <p class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-200 mb-4">What defines 'founding' members and sponsors?</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Anyone who joined The Space or supported us with sponsorship before we locked in a physical venue qualified as a founding supporter. Founding support eligiblity ended on 10/1/24 with our opening day.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <p class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-200 mb-4">Who runs The Space?</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">The Space is run by a member-elected Board of Directors. Board positions are filled annualy via member nominations and votes. The Board selects Officers that facilitate daily operations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <p class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-200 mb-4">Where does my money go?</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">All income from membership dues, donations, sponsors, ticketed events and other revenue streams are used to service our education mission and operational costs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <p class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-200 mb-4">How can I support The Space?</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">You can support The Space by becoming a member, attending events, making donations or sponsoring to further our initiatives.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <p class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-200 mb-4">What about alt-coins?</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">We're a bitcoin only organization. No distractions. We do, however, support and advocate for crypto developers to transition and build on top of bitcoin.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </Container>
  </div>

</Layout>